overview.en: The SML foundation is an operation team serving the global digital product technology development. Technologies with rich experience in digital technology, with a large number of industry technical experts and authoritative technical consultants, provide the underlying technology engine and scientific algorithm for more than many digital technology platforms worldwide.
overview.zh: SML基金会是一家服务于全球数码产品技术开发的运营团队。 具有丰富数码科技经验的技术，拥有大量的行业技术专家和权威技术顾问，为 全球超过诸多数码科技平台提供底层技术引擎和科学算法。
